@Pakhom, could you please use and set maintainer-approval with the bugzilla account who's email matches the one that is set in the port as MAINTAINER? 

There's nothing stopping anyone from creating a matchingusername@anydomain.tld to try to impersonate others

If you need or would like multiple bugzilla accounts merged, don't hesitate to create an issue in Services:Bug Tracker requesting the merge
